data.title: Portrait of UCLA professor Dr. John F. Kessel, Los Angeles, 1927-1939
data.meta_description: Access to this collection is generously supported by Arcadia funds.Portrait of UCLA professor Dr. John F. KesselDr. John F. Kessel was listed as UCLA's professor of zoology. He was frequently mentioned in the newspaper for his study of parasites.Text on negative sleeve: Kessell[sic], John F. Dr.Handwritten on negative: Dr. John F. Kessel
